5 5. Enter into any contracts or agreements determined by the
6 governing body to be necessary or convenient to implement the
7 provisions and effectuate the purposes of project plans;
8 6. Receive, from the federal government or the state, loans and
9 grants for, or in aid of a project and to receive contributions from
